      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOLLOWTHEACE (4) has been freshened again since coming from a wide barrier first up but has trialled nicely twice in that time so shod have come on. Races well-second up and is a two-time winner at this distance. THE STEEL DRAGON (7) put the writing on the wall with back-to-back placings before coming from a similar barrier and doing some work before finding the front and going on to score by 2m at Hamilton last time. Can go on with it. BIG SLEDGE HAMMER (6) worked from a tough barrier last time so prepared to overlook that result. Placed from a similar barrier to this here prior and had won three of his previous four starts so can bounce back. OZZIE CORKA (3) led from this barrier and stuck on to place at Wagga last start. Could give a sight again.",
